<entry colname='desc'><para>&FPA; source name for data directory for field to sample
</para><para>(Note: the format for this keyword would be <userinput><replaceable>source</replaceable></userinput> if the data directory has no sub sources, or <userinput><replaceable>source</replaceable>:<replaceable>subsource</replaceable></userinput> if the data directory has sub sources)
